From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Patric Stout <github@truebrain.nl>
Date: Sun, 5 Jul 2026 10:48:03 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 14/16] port: add basic support for Linux

This is a "bare minimum" port. It uses a stab as driver,
and no actual window is created.
